                                    <material>Stone</material> <objectType>pillar</objectType> comprised of <q>'spotted' dolerite from Carn Meini, Preseli Hills, 13km away.</q><bibl><ptr target ="EDW2007"/>Edwards 2007<citedRange unit="page">316</citedRange></bibl>.
